2DCFT is a 2D multiplayer capture the flag game.

Using a side-scrolling map, with different platforms to jump on (similar to Mario games) and 3 layers of blocks, so you can hide behind or in front of them while travlling accross the map.

Main Mechanics:
-Movement
-Attack of some sort to reset enemy player(s)
-Grabbing/Dropping the flag
-Score counting system.

The Js library we will use is: https://angularjs.org/
